cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.AI

This paper deals with the reconstruction of logic with interaction as a primitive notion, which falls under the category of mathematical logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the concept of paths, which is related to game semantics (cs.PL) and graph theory (cs.GT). The computational aspect of the paper, specifically the constructive way to capture the incarnation of a behavior, suggests a connection to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
